name: Trainer 1
Dialogue: You have POKEMON with you! You're mine!

name: Trainer 1 after
Dialogue: You need light to get through that dark tunnel ahead.

name: Trainer 2
Dialogue: Bwahaha! Great! I was bored, eh!

name: Trainer 2 after
Dialogue: You sure had guts standing up to me there, eh?

name: Trainer 3
Dialogue: Who's that walking with those good looking POKEMON?

name: Trainer 4
Dialogue: I got up early every day to raise my POKEMON from cocoons!

name: Trainer 4 after
Dialogue: I have to collect more than bugs to get stronger...

name: Trainer 5 after
Dialogue: If you don't like bug POKEMON, you bug me!

name: Trainer 6
Dialogue: I'm taking ROCK TUNNEL to go to LAVENDER...

name: Trainer 6 after
Dialogue: Are you off to ROCK TUNNEL too?

name: Trainer 7
Dialogue: Hahaha! Aren't you a little toughie!

name: Trainer 8 after
Dialogue: You're obviously talented! Good luck to you!

name: Trainer 9 after
Dialogue: Hahahaha! Us hearty guys always laugh!
